column4: i have a question about configuring my printer, I have a epson stylus c82. this printer isnt named in the printer setup wizard. i tried new-stylus-color-series, but printing a test site resulted in an empty page. what can i do?
to be honest, it had to shut off the printer to stop producing more empty pages.
install cupsys-driver-gimpprint-data and the right printer will appear in the list
